---
// src/components/Process.astro
import { base } from 'astro:config/client';
---

<header>
  <div class="container nav">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src={`${base}/favicon.png`} alt="Move-Ready Concierge Logo" width="56" height="56" />
      Move Ready Concierge
    </div>

    <nav id="navLinks">
      <a href={`${base}/`}>Home</a>
      <a href={`${base}about`}>About</a>
      <a href={`${base}process`}>How It Works</a>
      <a href={`${base}services`}>Services</a>
      <a href={`${base}/#contact`}>Contact</a>
      <a href={`${base}/#book`} class="btn-primary">Book Now</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="hamburger" id="hamburger"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
  </div>
</header>

<main>
  <section class="hero-process">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>How It Works</h1>
      <p>A simple, efficient three-step process designed to make your move stress-free.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>Our Process</h2>
      <p>From consultation to completion</p>
    </div>

    <div class="process-steps">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Consultation</h3>
          <p>
            We begin with a comprehensive consultation to understand your unique needs. During this phase, 
            we'll discuss your timeline, budget, specific requirements, and any concerns you may have. 
            This conversation allows us to create a personalized moving plan tailored exactly to your situation.
          </p>
          <ul class="step-details">
            <li>Initial assessment of your moving needs</li>
            <li>Timeline and budget discussion</li>
            <li>Special requirements identification</li>
            <li>Customized moving plan creation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Coordination</h3>
          <p>
            Once your plan is approved, we swing into action. Our team coordinates every aspect of your move, 
            from scheduling trusted movers to arranging cleaning services, junk removal, and any repairs needed. 
            You'll have a single point of contact throughout the entire process—no juggling multiple vendors.
          </p>
          <ul class="step-details">
            <li>Professional mover scheduling and management</li>
            <li>Cleaning service coordination</li>
            <li>Junk removal and hauling arrangements</li>
            <li>Regular updates and communication</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Execution</h3>
          <p>
            On moving day and beyond, we oversee every detail to ensure flawless execution. Our team manages 
            the timeline, coordinates all vendors, and handles any unexpected issues that arise. You can relax 
            knowing that professionals are managing every aspect of your move from start to finish.
          </p>
          <ul class="step-details">
            <li>On-site supervision and management</li>
            <li>Real-time problem solving</li>
            <li>Quality control throughout the process</li>
            <li>Final walkthrough and completion</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container timeline-section">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>What to Expect</h2>
      <p>Your move timeline from start to finish</p>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker">📅</div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h4>Week 1: Planning Phase</h4>
          <p>Initial consultation, assessment, and customized plan development. We'll provide you with a detailed timeline and cost breakdown.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker">🔧</div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h4>Week 2-3: Pre-Move Preparation</h4>
          <p>Vendor scheduling, packing coordination, and handling any repairs or cleaning needed at your current location.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker">🚚</div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h4>Moving Day: Execution</h4>
          <p>Professional movers handle the physical transition while we oversee every detail, ensuring everything goes according to plan.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker">✨</div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h4>Post-Move: Final Touches</h4>
          <p>Unpacking coordination, cleaning services at your new location, and any final adjustments needed to get you settled.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
      <p>The Move Ready advantage</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>🎯 Full Accountability</h3>
        <p>We take complete ownership of your move. If something goes wrong, we fix it—no passing the buck to other vendors.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>⏱️ Time Savings</h3>
        <p>No more spending hours researching movers, comparing quotes, or coordinating schedules. We handle it all.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>💰 Cost Transparency</h3>
        <p>Know exactly what you're paying from day one. No hidden fees, no surprise charges, just honest pricing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>🛡️ Peace of Mind</h3>
        <p>All our vendors are licensed, insured, and thoroughly vetted. Your belongings are in safe hands.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <div class="cta">
      <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p>Let's create your personalized moving plan today.</p>
      <a href={`${base}/#book`} class="btn-primary">Schedule Your Free Consultation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  <div class="container">© <span id="year"></span> Move Ready Concierge — Making your move feel like home</div>
</footer>

<script>
  const hamburger = document.getElementById('hamburger');
  const navLinks = document.getElementById('navLinks');
  const year = document.getElementById('year');

  if (hamburger && navLinks) {
    hamburger.addEventListener('click', () => {
      navLinks.classList.toggle('open');
    });
  }

  if (year) {
    year.textContent = new Date().getFullYear().toString();
  }
</script>

<style>
  :root {
    --primary: #1e3a5f;
    --accent: #f59e0b;
    --accent-light: #fbbf24;
    --accent-soft: rgba(245,158,11,0.12);
    --warm: #fffbeb;
    --warm-mid: #fef3c7;
    --bg: #ffffff;
    --muted: #64748b;
    --border: #e2e8f0;
    --radius: 20px;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: var(--primary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 4rem 1.25rem;
  }

  header {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.15);
    z-index: 1000;
  }

  .nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    height: 80px;
  }

  .logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  nav a:hover { 
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
    color: white;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.6rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(245,158,11,0.3);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(245,158,11,0.4);
  }

  .hamburger { display: none; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; cursor: pointer; }
  .hamburger span { width: 26px; height: 3px; background: var(--primary); border-radius: 4px; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    nav {
      position: absolute;
      top: 80px;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.98);
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      display: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    nav.open { display: flex; }
    .hamburger { display: flex; }
  }

  .hero-process {
    padding: 8rem 0 6rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #2d5a8f);
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-process h1 {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .hero-process p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  section { padding: 5.5rem 0; }

  .section-title { 
    text-align: center; 
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem; 
  }
  
  .section-title h2 { 
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.4rem; 
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  .section-title p { 
    color: var(--muted); 
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .process-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .step-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 3rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  }

  .step-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(245,158,11,0.15);
    border-color: var(--accent-soft);
  }

  .step-number {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(245,158,11,0.25);
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .step-content p {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .step-details {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .step-details li {
    color: var(--muted);
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.75rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .step-details li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .timeline-section {
    background: var(--warm);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .timeline {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 30px;
    top: 30px;
    bottom: 30px;
    width: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-item:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: white;
    border: 3px solid var(--accent);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .timeline-content {
    flex: 1;
    padding-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-content h4 {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(245,158,11,0.15);
    border-color: var(--accent-soft);
  }

  .card h3 {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .card p {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .cta {
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245,158,11,0.08), transparent),
      linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #2d5a8f);
    color: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 6rem 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(30,58,95,0.25);
  }

  .cta h2 { 
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.6rem; 
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  .cta p { 
    opacity: 0.95; 
    margin-bottom: 2.8rem;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
  }

  footer {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    background: #ffffff;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  ::selection {
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .step-card {
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .timeline::before {
      left: 30px;
    }

    .process-steps {
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>